   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Beinecke_1836_page01.jpg"/>
            <p>
                    As soon as I hear from Mess.rs <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BaldR1" cert="high">Baldwin</persName>
               <lb/>
                    and <persName ref="./Personography.xml#CradC1">Cradock</persName> I will let you know the result<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>If they should answer that they do<lb/>
               not desire to have <title ref="./Workography.xml#Helen1">Helen</title> till they are called<lb/>
               upon by the public for a new <choice>
                  <orig>Ed<hi rend="superscript">n.</hi>
                  </orig>
                  <reg>Edition</reg>
               </choice> of the<lb/>
                    whole collection of my tales &amp; novels, and<lb/>
                    if that should be at a distant period perhaps<lb/>
                    it may not interfere with your wishes<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>At all events you now know all that<lb/>
                    I have done or mean to do; and shall<lb/>
                    know as soon as I know more –<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>I have every reason to be satisfied <unclear>with</unclear>
               <lb/>
               your liberal <unclear>&amp;</unclear> fair dealing, and obliging<lb/>
                    conduct – and have so expressed myself<lb/>
               <add>of you</add> to others as well as to yourself<lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
                    I am Sir<lb/>
               Your <choice><orig>Obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</orig><reg>Obedient</reg></choice> Servant<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName><lb/>
               <address>
                  <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Beinecke_1836_page02.jpg"/>
                  <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BentR1">Richard Bentley Esq<hi rend="superscript">re</hi>
                  </persName>
                  <addrLine/>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Old-Burlington-Street_ENK">Old Burlington Street</placeName>
                  <addrLine/>
                  <addrLine/>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
   
